19
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,151
Did you two have a fight?

20
00:02:05,405 --> 00:02:09,655
Right, you have to prepare
extra delicious meat after a fight.

21
00:02:12,355 --> 00:02:15,580
Extra delicious meat...

22
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:26,090
What's this?

23
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:31,580
This is a special salt plate I prepared for today.

24
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:32,730
Rock salt?

25
00:02:32,730 --> 00:02:36,505
This board was cut from a large block of salt.

26
00:02:36,505 --> 00:02:39,330
We're going to grill the meat
directly on the salt plate today.

27
00:02:40,530 --> 00:02:41,516
Presenting...

28
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,880
The extra delicious meat!

29
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,656
<i>To be honest,</i>

30
00:02:56,505 --> 00:03:00,380
<i>Seeing that she didn't bring up what happened that night</i>

31
