If you overcook the tenderloin, it will become tough.

35
00:03:19,555 --> 00:03:22,380
Just make sure it's cooked through.

36
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,430
Let's eat!

37
00:03:37,805 --> 00:03:41,420
So tender, it melts in your mouth.

38
00:03:41,655 --> 00:03:43,907
The saltiness is just right.

39
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:46,855
It really brings out the natural sweetness of the meat.

40
00:03:51,730 --> 00:03:55,180
Using thick-cut meat was a good choice.

41
00:04:04,555 --> 00:04:08,330
This is even better than what
you'd get at a fancy restaurant!

42
00:04:22,205 --> 00:04:23,705
