53
00:05:45,205 --> 00:05:48,617
Sorry, the tenderloin is all gone.

54
00:05:49,055 --> 00:05:50,738
But it's no problem.

55
00:05:51,305 --> 00:05:52,705
Wait for me a moment.

56
00:05:52,705 --> 00:05:57,232
Don't bother...

57
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:07,055
It's great to see you doing well.

58
00:06:08,605 --> 00:06:09,955
Dad too.

59
00:06:13,455 --> 00:06:16,930
Does Kenta usually cook?

60
00:06:18,455 --> 00:06:21,855
I cook sometimes too.

61
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:30,407
It's really nice to have a barbecue in the courtyard.

62
00:06:31,355 --> 00:06:32,755
When the weather is nice,

63
00:06:32,755 --> 00:06:35,691
