64
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,594
I see.

65
00:06:38,330 --> 00:06:42,159
I've even learned to start a fire myself!

66
00:06:42,955 --> 00:06:44,655
You?

67
00:06:47,805 --> 00:06:50,655
