71
00:07:03,755 --> 00:07:06,173
It's shochu!
[*Japanese distilled liquor]

72
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:08,230
Dad, you're such a glutton!

73
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:10,130
Adding sparkling water makes it really refreshing.

74
00:07:12,130 --> 00:07:13,330
Well then...

75
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:18,334
Kenta-san, what are you doing?

76
00:07:19,005 --> 00:07:23,555
It's a light side dish that goes well with shochu.

77
00:07:24,105 --> 00:07:27,755
Chicken skewers,
cut into pieces and threaded onto bamboo sticks.

78
00:07:33,855 --> 00:07:35,849
Grill it slowly on a salt plate.

79
00:07:36,055 --> 00:07:41,470
Then, finely chop the perilla leaves.

80
00:07:41,730 --> 00:07:48,284
After the meat is cooked...

81
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:57,580
