82
00:07:57,805 --> 00:08:01,205
The perilla plum chicken skewers are ready!

83
00:08:03,530 --> 00:08:05,080
Please eat while it's hot.

84
00:08:05,112 --> 00:08:08,430
This looks so delicious!

85
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:14,180
Delicious!

86
00:08:14,180 --> 00:08:17,325
The saltiness of the rock salt is perfect.

87
00:08:17,555 --> 00:08:20,855
Paired with perilla and plum sauce, it's very refreshing.

88
00:08:20,855 --> 00:08:23,355
Great!

89
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:26,496
