00:08:46,805 --> 00:08:49,005
Cheers!

96
00:08:54,705 --> 00:08:56,670
This is really good!

97
00:08:56,780 --> 00:08:59,380
The aroma of sake lees is intoxicating,
and it goes down so smoothly.

98
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:00,955
Good!

99
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:04,680
I'm going to eat this with the chicken skewers.

100
00:09:16,555 --> 00:09:19,316
