114
00:10:44,355 --> 00:10:47,563
Chihiro is an only child.

115
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,177
And her mother passed away early.

116
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:53,005
Yes...

117
00:10:53,955 --> 00:10:59,905
I always stayed in the university,
buried in my research.

118
00:11:02,005 --> 00:11:03,580
I see.

119
00:11:06,305 --> 00:11:08,691
I made her pretty lonely before.

120
00:11:09,755 --> 00:11:12,825
Although I thought I was doing
my best to raise her with love,

121
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:19,055
