00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,555
Kenta-kun,

135
00:12:21,555 --> 00:12:24,630
Father-in-law,

136
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:27,030
Kenta-kun,

137
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:29,080
Father-in-law,

138
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,980
