150
00:13:45,405 --> 00:13:47,303
This is so good!

151
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:51,655
Father-in-law, you make a really good coffee.

152
00:13:51,655 --> 00:13:54,480
It's the only thing I'm good at.

153
00:13:55,973 --> 00:14:00,628
