169
00:15:33,530 --> 00:15:36,455
My dad also said he wanted to have a drink with you.

170
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:39,507
I should be thanking him...

171
00:15:39,705 --> 00:15:42,080
He gave me a lot of encouragement.

172
00:15:46,105 --> 00:15:49,405
Could you come to the courtyard when you're free?

173
00:15:51,955 --> 00:15:53,030
Okay.

174
00:16:01,905 --> 00:16:03,957
It's a home theater.

175
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:07,308
Of course, I also prepared popcorn.

176
00:16:17,930 --> 00:16:20,576
Welcome to the VIP seats.

177
00:16:21,530 --> 00:16:23,280
