186
00:17:35,497 --> 00:17:36,963
It happened,

187
00:17:38,776 --> 00:17:41,608
when I was in the second year of middle school...

188
00:18:00,341 --> 00:18:01,516
Senpai?

189
00:18:10,255 --> 00:18:12,908
Want to try a kiss?

190
00:18:14,005 --> 00:18:15,255
A kiss?

191
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:19,655
I guess not.

192
00:18:19,655 --> 00:18:25,005
<i>I really liked that senior back then.</i>

193
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:28,355
Okay.

194
00:19:07,305 --> 00:19:12,605
