195
00:19:15,705 --> 00:19:17,030
I guess so...

196
00:19:18,130 --> 00:19:21,630
<i>Then summer vacation started.</i>

197
00:19:21,630 --> 00:19:24,530
<i>I haven't seen her since then.</i>

198
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:30,387
