202
00:20:04,805 --> 00:20:09,805
The time we've spent together has been truly happy.

203
00:20:13,155 --> 00:20:19,182
But, this tremendous happiness...

204
00:20:20,905 --> 00:20:25,805
Makes me worry that it will disappear one day.

205
00:20:29,166 --> 00:20:31,266
I can't help but become anxious.

206
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:41,405
I keep dwelling on things from so long ago.

207
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:46,530
It's really embarrassing.

208
00:20:48,455 --> 00:20:50,480
Not at all.

209
00:20:54,205 --> 00:20:56,906
Feelings are very delicate.

210
00:20:58,380 --> 00:21:03,130
Everyone has their own unique struggles.

211
00:21:05,605 --> 00:21:07,180
Chihiro-san.

212
00:21:09,505 --> 00:21:14,458
I raelly like Kenta-san.

213
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,080
That's why,

214
00:21:19,147 --> 00:21:21,255
I'm not going anywhere.

215
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:30,505
It took us a long time to get here.

216
00:22:32,593 --> 00:22:33,680
I'm,

217
00:22:35,330 --> 00:22:38,405
suddenly starting to get nervous...

218
00:22:52,730 --> 00:22:54,694
Like I said...

219
00:22:55,830 --> 00:22:57,780
Happiness won't run away.

220
00:23:00,805 --> 00:23:02,405
I won't let happiness slip away.
